snippet.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Smash-Up - Leonardo vs Raving Rabbid vs Nightwatcher vs Fugitoid
snippet.description:
http://www.turtledojo.com/index.php

A battle with me using, Leonardo against Raving Rabbid, Nightwatcher, and Fugitoid at the Warehouse. Surprised that the Rabbid's made it into the game, though.

Enjoy!
